    "Artificial intelligence (AI) has rapidly become an integral part of our digital lives.",
    "Its capacity to simulate human intelligence, particularly in pattern recognition and decision-making, has transformed various sectors such as business, management, medicine, military, education, gaming, libraries, etc.",
    "The idea of creating AI systems in libraries dates back to 1990.",
